40|$|Focusing on the {{structural}} fiscal policy adjustments {{specifically in the}} field of tax and expenditure policy, this paper reviews the recent experience of the ASEAN countries in the area of <b>fiscal</b> policy <b>reform</b> and collects the major lessons that emerge from such endeavor. It reviews variations in broad fiscal aggregates as a background to {{the structural}} <b>fiscal</b> <b>reforms</b> and presents the tax policy reform of ASEAN countries. It also bestows some space on the changing size and composition of government expenditures in the region. ASEAN, fiscal policy...|$|R
